Enum Class MessageType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MessageType>
it.polimi.ingsw.am16.common.tcpMessages.MessageType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MessageType>, Constable
public enum MessageType extends Enum<MessageType>
Enum that contains the types of TCP messages that can be sent, both from the server to the client, and from the client to the server.
